--Control Statement : 

        Control the flow of Program based on boolean result generated by checking certain conditions
          - Condition (if , else , else if ladder, switch )
          - loop (while , do while )
          - branching ( transfer of control) : goto-label,jump 
                however multiple goto create ambiguity

          CONTROl STATEMENT:      
                - break : breaks the current process 
                - continue : break the current iteration5      
